      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this vehicle has been maintained to a rigorous standard. It offers a seamless blend of performance and reliability, representing an exceptional value proposition for the discerning driver. Experience the assurance of a well-cared-for machine that remains in commendable mechanical and aesthetic order, ready for immediate service.",
      "price": 32500.0,
